title: God Has Great Purpose For Your Life | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: God Has Great Purpose For Your Life | Victoria Osteen
description:
You have everything you need to make a difference in this world. Let’s reevaluate our lives and realize we are here to make an impact. God has an incredible purpose for your life! 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
